    <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="budget-guide-monthly-budget-best-strategy-expected">
      <span class="faq-q-text">Budget Guide Monthly Budget Best Strategy Expected Results $150-300 Boost 2-3 top posts per month 5,000-15,000 local impressions $300-600 Boost posts + 1 ongoing reach campaign 15,000-40,000 impressions + follower growth $600-1,000 Boost + reach + lead generation ads 40,000-80,000 impressions + direct leads $1,000+ Full funnel: awareness + retargeting + conversions Predictable lead flow Reel Ads vs. Carousel Ads</span>
      <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="budget-guide-monthly-budget-best-strategy-expected"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Reel Ads get higher reach and lower cost-per-impression. They work best for awareness and attracting new followers. Carousel Ads get higher click-through rates and work best for showcasing multiple services or portfolio pieces.</p></div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="1-posting-without-location-tags">
      <span class="faq-q-text">1. Posting Without Location Tags</span>
      <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="1-posting-without-location-tags"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Every post without a location tag is a missed opportunity. Location tags put your content on the Instagram Map and in local search results. It takes 3 seconds to add one. There is no reason to skip it.</p></div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="2-ignoring-dms-and-comments">
      <span class="faq-q-text">2. Ignoring DMs and Comments</span>
      <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="2-ignoring-dms-and-comments"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Instagram rewards engagement. When someone comments on your post and you do not reply, the algorithm notes that. Worse, you lose a potential customer. Reply to every comment and DM. Even a simple "Thank you!" keeps the conversation going.</p></div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="3-only-posting-polished-content">
      <span class="faq-q-text">3. Only Posting Polished Content</span>
      <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="3-only-posting-polished-content"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Perfection kills consistency. Local businesses that only post when they have a "perfect" photo end up posting once a month. Your audience wants to see real work, real people, and real moments. A shaky phone video of your team at work outperforms a stock photo every time.</p></div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="4-inconsistent-posting">
      <span class="faq-q-text">4. Inconsistent Posting</span>
      <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="4-inconsistent-posting"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>The algorithm rewards consistency. Posting 5 times in 1 week and then disappearing for 3 weeks tells Instagram your account is inactive. Stick to 3-4 posts per week, every week. Use a <a href="/best/social-media-automation-tools/">social media scheduling tool</a> if you struggle with consistency.</p></div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="5-not-using-reels">
      <span class="faq-q-text">5. Not Using Reels</span>
      <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="5-not-using-reels"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Reels get 2-3x the reach of any other format. Local businesses that skip Reels are leaving their biggest growth opportunity on the table. You do not need fancy editing. A simple before-and-after with trending audio takes 5 minutes to create.</p></div></div>
  </div>
