      <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="is-instagram-better-than-facebook-for-local-busine"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Instagram delivers higher engagement rates per post and reaches a younger demographic (18-44). Facebook has a larger total user base and better options for community groups. Most local businesses benefit from using both, but Instagram gives more organic reach per post with less effort.</p></div></div>
  </div>
